      "source": [
        "share_returns = np.log(share/share.shift(1))\r\n",
        "share_returns.dropna(inplace=True)\r\n",
        "stats = pd.DataFrame()\r\n",
        "stats['Annualized_Returns(%)'] =share_returns.mean() *semana*100\r\n",
        "stats['Annualized_Volatility(%)'] = share_returns.std() * np.sqrt(semana)*100\r\n",
        "stats['Sharpe_Ratio'] = stats['Annualized_Returns(%)'] /stats['Annualized_Volatility(%)']\r\n",
        "print(82*'-')\r\n",
        "print('Assets Classes Annualized Statistics â€” full observation period')\r\n",
        "stats.style.bar(color=['red','green'], align='zero')\r\n"
      ],
